Package: soilgraph
Title: Soil Profile Visualization from Field Descriptions
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        given = "Nicolás",
        family = "Riveras-Muñoz",
        email = "contact@nriveras.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    ))
Description: Build structured soil profile descriptions following a
    standardised field specification, export them to a versioned JSON schema,
    and render publication-ready visualisations with irregular coarse-fragment
    and horizon-boundary engines powered by 'ggplot2'. Follows Soil Taxonomy
    (USDA) vocabulary for texture, moisture, colour, boundary grade and shape,
    and coarse fragment properties.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://nriveras.github.io/soilgraph,
    https://github.com/nriveras/soilgraph
BugReports: https://github.com/nriveras/soilgraph/issues
